name: Ometepe
notes: True to form, I hiked this volcano in flip-flops. The guide's consternation gave way to grudging respect

name: Gunung Batur
notes: Beautiful volcano growing out of its own caldera, with multiple villages around a lake within the caldera.

name: Table Mountain
notes: Table Mountain and I bonded, especially when the covid pandemic hit, over the two-and-a-half weeks I spent booking flights home as the world closed down airspace, and canceled said flights.
